description: This header file defines APIs related to LAN management data model for COSA (Cloud Operating System Architecture) components. It declares functions for getting and setting parameters, as well as validation, commit, and rollback operations for device info related to LAN management.

methods.name: LanManagement_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value related to LAN management for device info.

methods.name: LanManagement_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value related to LAN management for device info.

methods.name: LanManagement_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value related to LAN management for device info.

methods.name: LanManagement_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value related to LAN management for device info.

methods.name: LanManagement_Validate
methods.description: Validates the current configuration or parameters before applying.

methods.name: LanManagement_Commit
methods.description: Commits the configuration changes made to LAN management.

methods.name: LanManagement_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back any uncommitted configuration changes for LAN management.
